Class CombinedIterator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucla.sspace.util.CombinedIterator<T>

    Iterator<T>

    public class CombinedIterator<T>
extends Object
implements Iterator<T>
    An Iterator implemntation that combines multiple iterators into a single instance.

    This class is thread-safe.
